metadata.name: Enigma #1
metadata.description:
Our mission at Enigma is to level the playing field through education and innovative social trading solutions.

All members of our discord community will have completely free access to trading and web3 education plus our BTC algorithm signals. Additionally, owning an Enigma NFT will provide access to our exclusive member benefits through the current year.

Member benefits include but are not limited to: fully automated copy trading access, wealth-building tools and life hacks, market analysis, and live trade calls.

Visit our website: [https://www.enigmanft.ai/](https://www.enigmanft.ai/) for more details.
